title: Charity & The JAMband - Party Like A Twinkle Star (FLAC)
description:
Charity & The JAMband - Party Like A Twinkle Star (2009)

FLAC


This is a two-disc collection of children's music from Charity and the JAMband. Disc 

one is for activity, disc two is for bedtime.


From the band:
 
"Party Like a Twinkle Star, our new release, comes with two CDs! You get: Party: 10 

Songs for Rocking Out AND Twinkle: 10 Song for Tucking In. As a collection, this 

double album showcases all the JAMband has to offer."


Disc One: Party - 

1.  Get Your Booty Out of Bed

2.  Pancakes

3.  Party

4.  Some More S'mores

5.  Row Row Row Your Boat

6.  Beach

7.  Rockstar

8.  Amazing Rocket Ship

9.  Into Space

10. We Are Stardust


Disc Two: Twinkle - 

1.  One Golden Bowl

2.  So Long to the Day

3.  A Little Night Music

4.  Moon Hug

5.  Song in Your Heart

6.  Rock-A-Bye

7.  The Reminder

8.  Twinkle Twinkle Little Star

9.  Juggle the Stars

10. The Bird


All MP3 tracks have ID3 tags for Album, Artist, Track Titles, and order in the album.  Some other information, such as Year, Genre, and Publisher may have been added if the information was available to me.


All albums will have album art included if it was available to me.

All MP3 files that I upload are encoded at TRUE 320 kbps.
